## Description {#details}

An invented name for a template parameter for which we don&#39;t have a corresponding template argument.

This node is created when parsing the &lt;lambda-sig&gt; for a lambda with explicit template arguments, which might be referenced in the parameter types appearing later in the &lt;lambda-sig&gt;.
